<h2 class="title">
  New CD copy protection method easily compromised
  
</h2>

<div id="top-actionbar" class="actionbar">
  
      <div class="topic-actions">
        <div class="reply-button"><a rel="nofollow" href="./posting.php?mode=reply&amp;f=2&amp;t=2377&amp;sid=79b8ac6f9bd9f08b8c549a52e30056f5"><img src="//cdn.arstechnica.net/civis/ars/imageset/en/button_topic_locked.png" alt="This topic is locked, you cannot edit posts or make further replies." title="This topic is locked, you cannot edit posts or make further replies." /></a></div>
        
      </div>
    
    <div class="pager">
      69 posts â€¢ <li class="selected">1</li><li><a href="http://arstechnica.com/civis/./viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=2377&amp;sid=79b8ac6f9bd9f08b8c549a52e30056f5&amp;start=40">2</a></li>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="./viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=2377&amp;sid=79b8ac6f9bd9f08b8c549a52e30056f5&amp;start=40">Next</a>
