        <tr>
          <td class="post-content">
            <div class="post-content-inner">
              
              Note: Autoplay != Autorun<BR><BR>Autoplay is where Windows takes a user-specified action when a CD/DVD is inserted. That's what makes the dialog box come up asking you if you want to browse the CD, play it, etc.<BR><BR>Autorun, which is what's being used here, is where Windows does what the autorun.inf file on the CD/DVD says it should do. That's what makes an installer run automatically when you insert the disk for an application that hasn't been installed yet, for example.<BR><BR>Autorun has been around since Windows 95, but Autoplay is more recent; I think it might be an XP thing.

              

              
              
            </div>
          </td>
        </tr>
        
    </table>
    
