              I think it's a great idea by BMG. Since these CDs are perfectly standard mixed-mode CDs, they play fine in anything. They just use software to restrict copying by an autorun procedure.<BR><BR>Most piracy is from AOLers running MusicMatch and Kazaa and this will prevent the majority of that.<BR><BR>Truly beautiful and, though this word is tremendously over used I find it approproiate here, actually innovative.<BR><BR>H@

              

              
              
